Maintainer: Matt Comben <matthew@dockstudios.co.uk>
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-libvirt, qemu, python3-lockfile, python3-texttable, python3-paramiko, python3-mako, libvirt-bin, python3-argcomplete, python3-netifaces, python3-pbkdf2, python3-ldap, python3-serial, mcvirt-common (=%VERSION%)
Recommends: git
Suggests: iotop, iftop, htop, drbd8-utils
Description: Virtualization host management utility.
 MCVirt is a tool for controlling VMs built around
 libvirt, using kvn backed virtualisation.
